# 🖥️ Shiny App — Kings Project Interactive Dashboard

This folder contains the source code and deployment link for the interactive Shiny app built for the Kings Project.

---

## 🎯 Purpose
The app allows users to:
- Explore international players by archetype, age, and performance metrics  
- Filter by percentile thresholds (e.g., elite rebounders, above-average defenders)  
- Visualize player clusters in 3D space (3-Point %, Defense %, NBA Probability)  

